{"tid":1301951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"社會信用評級再下一步係咩？ 係集中營","createTime":"2019-07-09T18:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T12:42:10.000Z","uid":18559,"like":212,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"c0c73959a8830c1a1806fe4140e9a722bde3b4ae","tid":1301951,"uid":18559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:59:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NrCbdPb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNrCbdPb.png&h=0f7cdf3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1945年新疆只係得<span style=\"color: red;\">6.2%</span>漢族人<br />\n到2008年漢族人足足升到<span style=\"color: red;\">39.2%</span><br />\n<br />\n中共好明顯用緊同一招對付香港 每日150直接溝淡香港人，之後？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6a6jnJW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6a6jnJW.png&h=3a4caac2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為被溝淡，2000年嘅時候，大部份新疆人只係可以做低下嘅工作例如耕田，而相對好啲嘅工就比漢族人搶哂<br />\n<br />\n去到2009年新疆人終於頂唔順 真．暴動，打鳩漢族人，做成200人死傷<br />\n<br />\n佢地得到嘅，就係所謂嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">police (甚至military)state</span>，行出行入都有軍隊，買把刀要實名，最恐怖就係<span style=\"color: red;\">集中洗腦營</span>，將中共認為係極端嘅思想不斷洗腦洗走，用愛國愛黨嘅思想取締。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cMkHcZ5IwjU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcMkHcZ5IwjU&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBMVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=6d0d95c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cMkHcZ5IwjU</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WmId2ZP3h0c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWmId2ZP3h0c&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBMVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=b19bca5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WmId2ZP3h0c</a><br />\n<br />\n我講嘅都係由係呢2條片到睇到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日新疆，明日香港，今次真係要一鼓作氣，乜撚野都反哂佢，就算長期抗爭都唔好蝕左度氣，推倒個政府</span></span>"},{"pid":"7fe5dea367717d4ee446bf22c3909ba732d62486","tid":1301951,"uid":18559,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T19:01:57.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，片入面啲人隻眼